feel the guilt and keep going.

00:08:55.687 --> 00:08:56.520 align:middle line:90%
And I do keep going.

00:08:56.520 --> 00:08:57.660 align:middle line:90%
And then I leave it behind.

00:08:57.660 --> 00:09:00.202 align:middle line:84%
And you know what the other--
then all kinds of gifts emerge.

00:09:00.202 --> 00:09:03.190 align:middle line:84%
Like, for example, I might
have been right so much

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:05.190 align:middle line:84%
