00:09:06.590 --> 00:09:09.900 align:middle line:10%
So to step aside and go out for
a walk gives me perspective.

00:09:09.900 --> 00:09:12.565 align:middle line:84%
I can come back and rewrite the
whole thing in much less time

00:09:12.565 --> 00:09:14.190 align:middle line:84%
