Really the lesson is
sacrifice need not

00:22:52.300 --> 00:22:53.920 align:middle line:90%
be a synonym for kindness.

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:56.980 align:middle line:84%
And that is the bottom line that
Holly wanted to share with us,

00:22:56.980 --> 00:23:00.000 align:middle line:84%
coming home to ourselves,
self care, soul care.

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:02.057 align:middle line:84%
I'm so pleased that you
could be with us today,

00:23:02.057 --> 00:23:02.890 align:middle line:90%
"Living in Balance."

00:23:02.890 --> 00:23:03.690 align:middle line:90%
I'm Shakti-Hill.

00:23:03.690 --> 00:23:07.490 align:middle line:84%
And will you please learn to
live in balance in mind, body,

00:23:07.490 --> 00:23:08.290 align:middle line:90%
and spirit.

00:23:08.290 --> 00:23:11.260 align:middle line:84%
Until next time, may you be
well, happy, and peaceful.

